The paper deals with visual steganography techniques for hiding a full-sized color image/video within another. This involves the use of deep convolutional neural networks and the modeling of temporal residuals between consecutive video frames. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with security and cryptography, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of deep learning models suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) as another possible category. The paper also involves the use of multimedia data, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia).
